				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You also don't want to use ShowDialog to show your main form. You want to use Application.Run(Window1). The difference is subtle, and probably won't cause issues is most cases, but you could conceivably run into some problems that aren't easily traced back to the fact that you used ShowDialog instead of Application.Run.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

