					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I created an empty VB.NET project in order to do this. Here is some code.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Imports System<br />Imports System.Drawing<br />Imports System.Drawing.Color<br /><br />Imports System.Windows.Forms<br /><br />Class Module1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Public Class Form1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Inherits System.Windows.Forms.Form<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Public X As Integer = 0<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Shared Sub Main()<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dim Window As New Form1()<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.Width = Screen.PrimaryScreen.Bounds.Width / 2<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.Height = Screen.PrimaryScreen.Bounds.Height / 2<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.Text = &quot;Untitled v1&quot;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.BackColor = Gray<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.FormBorderStyle = FormBorderStyle.Sizable<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.MaximizeBox = True<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.MinimizeBox = True<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.StartPosition = FormStartPosition.Manual<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Window.Location = New Point(Screen.PrimaryScreen.Bounds.Width / 4, Screen.PrimaryScreen.Bounds.Height / 4)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Application.Run(Window)<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; MessageBox.Show(&quot;120!&quot;)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; End Sub<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Protected Overrides Sub WndProc(ByRef m As Message)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Select Case (m.Msg)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Case Else<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; X = X + 1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; If X = 120 Then<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; X = 0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; End If<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; End Select<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; MyBase.WndProc(m)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; End Sub<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; End Class<br />End Class</div></div>

					
